fly away home ( a.k.a. flying wild and father goose ) is a 1996 family comedy-drama film directed by carroll ballard . the film stars anna paquin , jeff daniels and dana delany . fly away home was released on september 13 , 1996 by columbia pictures . fly away home dramatizes the actual experiences of bill &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; who , in 1986 , started training canadian geese to follow his &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; aircraft , and succeeded in leading their migration in 1993 through his program " operation migration . " the film is also based on the experience of dr. william &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , a british-born zoologist and adventurer , who aided &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; with the migration .